him out now and to present him

00:14:03.270 --> 00:14:06.130
with the first John W. Kluge prize

00:14:06.130 --> 00:14:08.130
for lifetime achievement
in the human sciences.

00:14:08.130 --> 00:14:11.510
Ladies and gentlemen,
